# Example: provision a LibreChat prompt.
# Copy this file to <LIBRECHAT_PROMPTS_DIR>/my-prompt.md and adjust as needed.
---
name: Document Summary                           # displayed name in the prompt library
category: Productivity                           # prompt category
command: summarize                               # /slash-command trigger (no leading slash)
oneliner: Summarize a document in one paragraph  # short description shown in the UI
author_email: admin@example.com                  # optional; falls back to the ADMIN user
---
Summarize the following document in one concise paragraph, highlighting the key points and main conclusions:

{{document}}
